{"word":"G5468 - χαλιναγωγέω - chalinagōgéō - khal-in-ag-ogue-eh'-o - Bridle","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">χαλιναγωγέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">chalinagōgéō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">khal-in-ag-ogue-eh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Bridle</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - அடக்கு"},{"paragraph":"to lead by a bridle, to guide"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From a compound of <a href=\"#/G5469 - χαλινός - chalinós - khal-ee-nos'/5469\">G5469</a> and the reduplicated form of <a href=\"#/G71 - ἄγω - ágō - ag'-o/71\">G71</a>; to <i>be</i> a <i>bit leader</i>, that is, to <i>curb</i> (figuratively): - bridle.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}